@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vxnkbl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.95) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.65)) / wp.abs((v0 + 0.97 / v2 + 0.91)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = wp.sin(v0)
    v2 = v0
    v1 = wp.exp(v1)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.14) - (v1 + 0.62 - v0 + 0.45)) / (0.01 + wp.exp(v2 + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
